info.author: RobotPy Development Team
info.description:
RobotPy WPILib
==============

Python version of WPILib - the standard library used for programming FRC
robots.

Installation
============

Typically, you don't install this directly, but use the RobotPy installer
to install it on your roboRIO, or it is installed by pip as part of the
pyfrc setup process.

info.html_description:
RobotPy WPILib

Python version of WPILib - the standard library used for programming FRC robots.

Installation

Typically, you don’t install this directly, but use the RobotPy installer to install it on your roboRIO, or it is installed by pip as part of the pyfrc setup process.
